Looking at the documents, the 2016 TaxSlayer Bowl (December) was played at EverBank Field in Jacksonville, Florida. The document mentions that the stadium was renamed EverBank Field in 2010 after a naming rights deal with EverBank. Before that, it was known as Alltel Stadium from 1997 to 2006, and before that, probably Gator Bowl Stadium. 

So the current name at the time of the 2016 game was EverBank Field, which was established in 2010. The user is asking when the field assumed that specific name, so the answer should be 2010. The other documents also confirm that the agreement was extended in 2014, but the original name change was in 2010. Therefore, the correct answer is 2010.
